onverge.-Credit-Medios-y-MediaGetty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Jacob-Bannon-of-Converge.-Credit-Medios-y-MediaGetty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Jacob-Bannon-of-Converge.-Credit-Medios-y-MediaGetty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Jacob-Bannon-of-Converge.-Credit-Medios-y-MediaGetty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Jacob-Bannon-of-Converge.-Credit-Medios-y-MediaGetty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Jacob-Bannon-of-Converge.-Credit-Medios-y-MediaGetty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>美国硬核退伍军人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/converge">Converge</a>发行了一张新的现场专辑，为飓风海伦救援工作筹集资金。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/heriot-the-cover-interview-devoured-by-the-mouth-of-hell-3798080"><em>NME – 封面</em>：赫瑞特已准备好掀起地狱</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末，乐队在社交媒体上宣布了这张专辑，名为“Live in Orlando, FL 03.14.22”。该专辑于 2022 年 3 月在佛罗里达州奥兰多修道院录制，包含 18 首歌曲，包括《Under Duress》、《I Can Tell You About Pain》和《Concubine》。</p><p>该专辑现已通过 Bandcamp 发行 -<a href="https://dthw.sh/convergelive" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处向该事业捐款并收听该专辑</a>。</p><p>根据乐队的声明，这张现场专辑“旨在为受飓风海伦影响的人们提供经济援助”。 Converge 还确认“本次发布的所有收益将捐赠给互助救灾组织”——<a href="https://mutualaiddisasterrelief.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处了解有关该组织的更多信息</a>。</p><p>请参阅下面的完整帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAvkvQvtL_T/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;